data.title: The Avengers Episode List
data.meta_description: The Avengers episode list - Read online for free. The document summarizes the first two series of the 1960s British TV show The Avengers. It provides details on the episodes of Series 1, noting that very few full episodes still exist from the original broadcasts. It then summarizes the cast changes for Series 2, where Patrick Macnee became the lead alongside different female partners in each episode. Honor Blackman joined as a regular partner Cathy Gale.
